### BEGIN INIT INFO
# Provides: csgo-server
# Required-Start: $remote_fs $syslog
# Required-Stop: $remote_fs $syslog
# Default-Start: 2 3 4 5
# Default-Stop: 0 1 6
# Short-Description: CS:GO Multi-Mode Server Manager
### END INIT INFO

